data.description: Immaculately maintained home in West Pointe Gardens with elegant design and charming details throughout! The bright open floor plan begins with the formal dining area and spacious foyer with coved ceiling. The kitchen is a culinary haven, featuring modern appliances, granite countertops, glass tile backsplash, and a convenient breakfast bar overlooking the family room and breakfast area. The split floor plan design provides a tranquil retreat for the primary bedroom with a tray ceiling and an en-suite bathroom with double vanities, walk-in closet, and an oversized walk-in shower with glass block details. Covered patio overlooking the fully fenced backyard. Great location provides easy access to US-90, Loop 1604, Lackland, SeaWorld and plenty of shopping and restaurants!
